These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, domino, snooker
House: victorian, palace, ranch-style, colonial
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indonesian, spanish, italian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, martial-arts, western
 1. the italian is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing domino is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the palace house##1
 5. the person playing snooker is the colonial house##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the spanish is between the person watching satire movies and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the french##1
10. the person watching satire movies is between the spanish and the colonial house##2
11. the victorian house is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
12. the italian is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Game      | snooker        | canasta       | domino  | poker |
| House          | colonial     | ranch-style         | palace     | victorian    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Nationality           | indonesian | french | spanish   | italian     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Movie-Genre         | western     | satire     | zombie  | martial-arts       |

