 3. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is between the person playing snooker and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing bellflower##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the person who growsmarigold##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growsmarigold##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
13. the game-smoker is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
