.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, camping, skydiving
4 different games are played: poker, bridge, monopoly, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, pop, salsa, soul
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, farmhouse, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, baseball, climbing, biathlon
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of soul is between the person playing poker and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 7. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
 9. the art-deco house is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person playing bridge is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is climbing##1
13. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda        | milk     | cola        | fanta    |
| Hobby          | camping     | traveling   | collecting   | skydiving |
| Game           | mah-jongg | poker  | bridge | monopoly |
| Music-Genre   | pop            | salsa    | soul        | ambient  |
| House   | farmhouse          | futuristic | art-deco      | gothic-revival  |
| Sport           | baseball          | basketball     | biathlon      | climbing      |

