.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, photography, skydiving
City: berlin, new-york, hannover, boston
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue, blue, mauve
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower, balloon-flower, begonia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, cricket, golf, cycling
 1. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person traveling to hannover is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk        | coffee      | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Hobby         | photography | board-games | skydiving   | dancing   |
| City           | hannover | boston     | new-york        | berlin   |
| Color   | light-blue     | mauve    | purple | blue    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower      | bellflower      | begonia      | poppy |
| Sport           | rowing      | cricket    | cycling       | golf  |

