.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, drama, spy, mystery
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, carrot, kale, kiwi
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, freelancer, pilot, security-guard
City: hamburg, liverpool, miami, rome
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, mauve, lilac, lavender
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, sunflower, lily
 1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the pilot##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the chef is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is between the person who likes emerald and the person who growstulip##2
 9. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person who growsazalea is the security-guard##1
12. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to hamburg is between the chef and the person who growsazalea##2
14. the security-guard is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |       3        |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery      | scientific | drama       | spy   |
| Food          | carrot   | kale          | kiwi           | blueberry |
| Job           | chef     | freelancer    | security-guard | pilot     |
| City   | rome   | hamburg          | liverpool         | miami     |
| Color   | mauve    | emerald      | lavender       | lilac    |
| Flower           | lily | sunflower       | azalea         | tulip  |

