.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bolivar, davidoff, fonseca
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, white, lavender, azure
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, social-worker, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, satire, time-travel
4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, monopoly, chess
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, daffodil, poppy
 1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the social-worker##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is between the writer and the bartender##2
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fisherman##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the person who likes white is between the person who growsbellflower and the person playing billiard##2
 7. the person who growspoppy is between the person playing canasta and the person who growszinnia##2
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person who likes lavender is the writer##1
11. the fisherman is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
13. the person playing monopoly is the blend-smoker##1
14. the person who likes white is the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar          | fonseca     | davidoff        | bolivar         | blend   |
| Color         | aquamarine     | lavender     | white    | azure |
| Job           | fisherman  | writer      | social-worker | bartender   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | time-travel | satire        | crime       |
| Game   | chess    | billiard     | canasta    | monopoly     |
| Flower     | zinnia | poppy       | daffodil         | bellflower         |

