.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rat, pony, lizard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, september, july, may
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, funk, gospel, rock
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, electrician, manager, social-worker
House: cottage, craftsman, cape-cod, tower
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, russian, thai
 1. the tower house is on the right of the manager##1
 2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the mexican is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the pakistani##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the accountant##1
 7. the electrician is on the right of the accountant##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the cottage house##1
 9. the fan of gospel is the russian##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the electrician##1
11. the owner of the rat is on the left of the fan of funk##1
12. the fan of funk is between the owner of the lizard and the manager##2
13. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |       4       |
| Pet      | rat | pony         | lizard       | hamster         |
| Birthday          | january | september  | july        | may         |
| Music-Genre         | gospel | funk | r&b     | rock   |
| Job           | manager | accountant  | electrician | social-worker |
| House   | cape-cod  | tower     | craftsman       | cottage   |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani   | thai        | mexican       |

