.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, soul, folk
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, accountant, mechanic, dressmaker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, azalea, zinnia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, june, january
 1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
 3. the journalist is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the dressmaker is the fan of reggae##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of folk##1
 9. the accountant is the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the dressmaker is on the right of the mechanic##1
11. the person who growszinnia is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
12. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the fan of soul##1
13. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite     | mirinda  | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre          | jazz     | soul     | reggae | folk  |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | filmmaking | fishing  | sudoku   |
| Job   | accountant         | mechanic   | dressmaker   | journalist |
| Flower         | aconite       | azalea    | zinnia   | daffodil |
| Birthday     | january        | december   | june   | april      |

 